headline: Ark Invest Buys $16.5M of Coinbase Stock, Largest Purchase Since Aug. 1
summary: COIN closed at $264.97, 4.27% higher on the day, accompanying a relative recovery in the crypto market, which saw bitcoin gain over 3.3% to reclaim $90,000.
